00:03:45.080 --> 00:03:50.460
native graphical user interfaces in Python, and targeting that at desktop platforms,

00:03:50.460 --> 00:03:56.960
so Windows, Linux, macOS, but also mobile platforms, iOS and Android, the web as a GUI

