00:14:23.030 --> 00:14:25.620
There are a lot of things that probably should be progressive web apps

00:14:25.780 --> 00:14:28.700
that are, you know, or that could be progressive web apps.

00:14:29.540 --> 00:14:32.840
But that doesn't mean that there's no market for native apps

