I see which side fence you come down on.

00:28:03.290 --> 00:28:03.680
I got it.

00:28:04.080 --> 00:28:04.200
Yep.

00:28:04.440 --> 00:28:05.780
No, it's all good.

00:28:05.880 --> 00:28:06.380
I'm with you.

00:28:06.460 --> 00:28:06.740
I'm with you.

